<h2> Welcome to the quiz list!</h2>
<h5> i still can't believe that quiz only takes one z in english, according to my ide...</h5>
<h2> You may play any of these quiz if you're logged in</h2>
<h3>Each quiz has 5 questions, only contains one right answer. The other answers are automatically generated by the <a href="https://pokeapi.co/">PokeApi!</a> </h3>

<div class="list-group w-75 m-auto">
  <% @Quiz.each do | t | %>
    <a href="<%= "/quizz/#{t.id}" %>" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action d-flex gap-3 py-3" aria-current="true">
      <div class="d-flex gap-2 w-100 justify-content-between">
        <div>
          <h6 class="mb-0"><%= t.title %></h6>
          <p class="mb-0 opacity-75">Find the correct generations of each <%= t.theme %>!</p>
        </div>
        <small class="opacity-50 text-nowrap">t.timestamps</small>
      </div>
    </a>
  <% end %>

</div>
